pointSchemas.name: Circulating Marketcap
pointSchemas.description: The market capitalization of the asset, calculated using the circulating supply

pointSchemas.name: Circulating Marketcap Dominance
pointSchemas.description: The market capitalization of the asset as a percentage of the total market capitalization of all crypto assets

pointSchemas.name: Fully Diluted Marketcap
pointSchemas.description: The market capitalization of the asset, calculated using the fully diluted supply. Commonly known as Fully Diluted Valuation (FDV).
